==========
 INFOITEM 
==========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

also known as factoids .. info can be retrieved by keyword or searched

| 

  information items .. keyword/description pairs 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *info-forget (forget)*

    :description: forget <item> containing <txt>

    :permissions: FORGET .. OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !info-forget dunk bla
        <output> delete bla of dunk failed


2) *info-sd (sl)*

    :description: info-sd <txt> ..  search description of infoitems

    :permissions: USER .. WEB .. CLOUD

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !info-sd http
        <output> none found


3) *info-si (si)*

    :description: info-si <txt> ..  search the infoitems keys

    :permissions: USER .. WEB .. CLOUD

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !info-si test
        <output> none found


4) *info-size*

    :description: show number of infoitems

    :permissions: USER .. WEB .. CLOUD

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !info-size
        <output> we have 0 infoitems



regular expressions
-------------------
| 

1) ^(.+?)\s+=\s+(.+)$
      <keyword> = <description> .. add information item 
2) ^(.+)\?$
      <keyword>? .. ask for information item description 
3) ^\?(.+)$
      <keyword>? .. ask for information item description 
